{"tid":1393901,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【包生仔懶人教學】申請成為陪審員","createTime":"2019-08-01T08:43:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-04T10:11:18.000Z","uid":255155,"like":56,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"0dd6482103355dea8f4e8b080fa644a6be11c205","tid":1393901,"uid":255155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:43:44.000Z","msg":"受阿叔 <span style=\"color: red;\">已戒瞓覺</span> 啟發，今日嘗試打電話去28254668 check自己係唔係個陪審員list度，相信係好多人都一齊打呢個電話，所以打勁多次先有職員接聽電話。<br />\n如果你未打或者打去冇人聽，請你不妨睇睇自己係咪同下面個case一樣：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 大學／大專畢業<br />\n2. 近呢幾年從未改過屋企地址<br />\n3. 從未收過有關成為陪審員嘅信件<br />\n＝ 你不在陪審員名單之中</span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果你中咗上面幾項，你可以打電話check嘅時間都慳返，直接做以下四步：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 寫信表示你想做陪審員【參下文template】<br />\n2. 填好ROP18份表【參下文下載Link】<br />\n3. 你的畢業證書副本<br />\n4. 寄「香港灣仔告士打道七號入境事務大樓1201室陪審團登記小組」</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">書信template：</span></span><br />\n香港灣仔告士打道七號<br />\n入境事務大樓1201室<br />\n陪審團登記小組<br />\n執事先生鈞鑒：<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><ins>陪審員申請書</ins></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你好，本人於近日向主理陪審團事務書記辦事處查詢自己是否在陪審員名單，發現自己不在名單之中。然，出任陪審員乃是所有合乎資格的香港居民應盡之責。身為香港人，本人希望力盡公民責任，故特此函達申請成為陪審員。<br />\n<br />\n本人陳大文（Chan Tai Man），香港身份證號碼（A123456(7)），出生日期（04/06/1989），現申請成為陪審員，隨函附上表格ROP18及本人之最高學歷證明文件副本。如有任何查詢，歡迎致電1234-5678或電郵chantaiman@gmail.com與本人聯絡。謝謝。<br />\n<br />\n敬祝<br />\n鈞祺<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\">＿＿＿＿＿＿＿（簽署）<br />\n陳大文謹啟<br />\n</div><br />\n二零一九年八月一日<br />\n附件一：表格ROP18<br />\n附件二：學歷證明文件副本<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">ROP18表格下載Link</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.immd.gov.hk/pdforms/rop18.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.immd.gov.hk%2Fpdforms%2Frop18.pdf&d=H0od%2FlU2Kx31F%2BxGtrrl55KGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=ecb3b5a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.immd.gov.hk/pdforms/rop18.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n附埋另一個關於陪審員post！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【一張圖睇晒】阿叔提提你，唔一定係要大學先做到陪審員！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1392543\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1392543</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"bf2bb3da90ceb7c423804e7194c8e062b57e7096","tid":1393901,"uid":255155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:44:07.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"552d102e62d5e3c3f48afc2ab4d55a003dcfe176","tid":1393901,"uid":128870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:45:30.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"fd10a425aa527d25015ef2099ed26e109beac9db","tid":1393901,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:45:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"db4035317f1e30b3ce65fc2930d96d8e6c1074b3","tid":1393901,"uid":5627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:45:51.000Z","msg":"Thx 樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">推呀</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n----------------------------------------<br />\n[極重要] 聽日開始全民查閱選民登記冊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1392328\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1392328</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"150a7226207f4f36a2e5c7ff5a8d0bd56fda868f","tid":1393901,"uid":255155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:46:03.000Z","msg":"自膠頭先開咗去政事台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"915945082faffb6cd53028137266ee95dfe5aac6","tid":1393901,"uid":255155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:51:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跪求大家花少少時間，申請做陪審員，香港人要未雨綢繆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n改返啲資料、填好表格，加信封同幾蚊郵票<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e68260675dce5c317428c68b91ad806634f38b7","tid":1393901,"uid":255155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:54:52.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"a1251d9cc98eba2d5f8cdad0863eda5cba5ffbdc","tid":1393901,"uid":262043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:57:18.000Z","msg":"一年前on99咁簽咗份豁免信, 仲有冇得救?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b733d209f17d4f3743bdf685ce0e2d2843994171","tid":1393901,"uid":61536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1251d9cc98eba2d5f8cdad0863eda5cba5ffbdc","tid":1393901,"uid":262043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:57:18.000Z","msg":"一年前on99咁簽咗份豁免信, 仲有冇得救?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:07:45.000Z","msg":"再用嗰三部曲申請過！"},{"pid":"d3fd952274c6e099a599686b3e759feb0c4cb6c1","tid":1393901,"uid":255155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1251d9cc98eba2d5f8cdad0863eda5cba5ffbdc","tid":1393901,"uid":262043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:57:18.000Z","msg":"一年前on99咁簽咗份豁免信, 仲有冇得救?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:07:53.000Z","msg":"照做上面四步！你合資格，要去盡公民責任係理所當然嘅事啦～<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1610b08184df0e12953358c576e746896e00cfde","tid":1393901,"uid":255155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:09:13.000Z","msg":"推到人人都登記做陪審員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32db52d11601bafc3ae1a6d4809af02a61ce1126","tid":1393901,"uid":253954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:17:34.000Z","msg":"我都覺得奇怪<br />\nUG畢左業5年,PG畢左業2年<br />\n從來都無收過一封陪審員信<br />\n反而我細妹一UG畢業就收到信<br />\n我仲以為係因為佢讀social science先有資格<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24311a5090b31f22eae167675d6ad6e05cb8d56c","tid":1393901,"uid":35215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:27:46.000Z","msg":"多謝你！！！！！！"},{"pid":"aae887650e9141037514913f55ab9b4c51db0a8f","tid":1393901,"uid":255155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"32db52d11601bafc3ae1a6d4809af02a61ce1126","tid":1393901,"uid":253954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:17:34.000Z","msg":"我都覺得奇怪<br />\nUG畢左業5年,PG畢左業2年<br />\n從來都無收過一封陪審員信<br />\n反而我細妹一UG畢業就收到信<br />\n我仲以為係因為佢讀social science先有資格<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:28:12.000Z","msg":"快啲申請返啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地都有陪審員的資格架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">任何具備下列條件的香港居民，均有資格出任陪審員：<br />\n年滿21歲但未滿65歲；<br />\n精神健全而並無任何使其不能出任陪審員的情況如聽覺或視覺的損傷等；<br />\n品格良好；<br />\n熟悉聆訊時所採用的語言&mdash; 即中文或英文（視乎個別情況而定）</span></span>"},{"pid":"917e50ef8e42256d41ba210697b354b442507ebc","tid":1393901,"uid":255155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:34:35.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n天主教或基督教的宣誓誓詞：<br />\n本人，謹對全能上帝宣誓，本人將根據本案之證據，作出符合事實之裁決。<br />\nI (name in full) swear by Almighty God that I will give a true verdict in this case according to the evidence.<br />\n<br />\n非宗教式的宣誓誓詞：<br />\n本人（全名），謹鄭重至誠據實聲明，本人當以不懼、不偏、無私的精神，盡本人所知所能，聆聽證供，並作出真實的裁決。<br />\nI (name) solemnly, sincerely, and truly declare and affirm that I will give a true verdict in this case according to the evidence.<br />\n<br />\n雖然係HK01，但都可以聽下蕭叔叔條英文宣誓聲帶學習學習！<br />\n<a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/hk01company/vzkqkijx9em9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoundcloud.com%2Fhk01company%2Fvzkqkijx9em9&d=H0od%2FlU2Kx31F%2BxGtrrl55KGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=3ab82320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/hk01company/vzkqkijx9em9</a><br />\n</span></strong>"},{"pid":"1b789f97ef7c2533f84e55b94060357df9f65c43","tid":1393901,"uid":24591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:37:07.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"0e734fb26c851b7c7a9641778f87fbd36305a23b","tid":1393901,"uid":289719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:39:32.000Z","msg":"再推佢老味先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98531eb1f38cdffbf5173485145df4cc03377ba9","tid":1393901,"uid":255155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24311a5090b31f22eae167675d6ad6e05cb8d56c","tid":1393901,"uid":35215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:27:46.000Z","msg":"多謝你！！！！！！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:40:40