得?"},{"pid":"300e851a5376b0944d2ccc9ff7ce052704bfc421","tid":1393901,"uid":61481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T04:01:29.000Z","msg":"英文唔太好，有冇得做？？"},{"pid":"cb0fcb984f0f25a671be746c3ab0e6906bd58095","tid":1393901,"uid":42691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:05:39.000Z","msg":"入去睇完指引  開去活動台啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n指示越清楚越好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最好一樓就可以做任務<br />\n說明呀背景呀個d可以擺二樓<br />\n<br />\n現在正式徵用[活動台]作為[任務台]！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1396734\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1396734</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"175390936ac7084d4038fb8b775ef31b8fe3e9b8","tid":1393901,"uid":255155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bcd1cd297abf27695b61f5f3b0dde9cf7065aece","tid":1393901,"uid":13160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:36:19.000Z","msg":"Lm"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:11:41.000Z","msg":"#我要做陪審員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cb24b35beb915964159a13f156e78462f56cace","tid":1393901,"uid":255155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df4868c695c18745a26198e0efe926e93cdd852d","tid":1393901,"uid":63093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T17:23:22.000Z","msg":"8月5日罷工<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></strong></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:12:08.000Z","msg":"#我要罷工<br />\n#我要做陪審員"},{"pid":"05fe2b7e2662edac71f19361ec0cace275127289","tid":1393901,"uid":255155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf1aa96d4c33a87d0507527eca7fc63b948f225c","tid":1393901,"uid":71009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T17:39:24.000Z","msg":"未畢業係咪無得做"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:19:18.000Z","msg":"照寄信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用你中學／DSE cert做最高學歷證明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c742cf27294b017c04fb54dfea033d1055da03a","tid":1393901,"uid":255155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d208cc53b5fbacd9ef808890d405511f87ce6c3","tid":1393901,"uid":169687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T22:20:01.000Z","msg":"其實點解會講到要有大學學歷先做得陪審員？上面巴打條片無講，我上官網都無寫學歷要求只無話識中英<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y4EXgPC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY4EXgPC.png&h=ea786852&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:26:04.000Z","msg":"我都check咗，的確<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔一定要大學定大專學歷先做到</span></span>。<br />\n只係一直以來聽都係大學畢業後自動入池做陪審員，但事實唔係，有人會大學畢業後收到信通知入list，但有更多人冇收到，所以就開咗依個post，呼籲大家申請。<br />\n有誤導嘅位，對唔住！<br />\n再呼籲！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">全民做申請做陪審員，人人寄信登記</span></strong></span><br />\n夠<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">21歲嘅香港人</span></span>，請你地寄信申請時夾埋你地<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最高學歷證明</span></span>（如DSE證書／畢業證書）"},{"pid":"43ba2b11269d1313cf93cfa5baf2998411ad3084","tid":1393901,"uid":255155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52cae4482ff16917ef8ddca4b5025caa8093407d","tid":1393901,"uid":226393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T04:00:06.000Z","msg":"外國(英國)u grad一樣申請得?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:28:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">任何具備下列條件的香港居民，均有資格出任陪審員：<br />\n年滿21歲但未滿65歲；<br />\n精神健全而並無任何使其不能出任陪審員的情況如聽覺或視覺的損傷等；<br />\n品格良好，及<br />\n熟悉聆訊時所採用的語言&mdash; 即中文或英文（視乎個別情況而定）</span></span><br />\n<br />\n你具備上面條件，邊度畢業你都可以申請架～<br />\n記住信、表格、最高學歷證明副本"},{"pid":"be928af57ac4f1835e820cf16350a559547653e3","tid":1393901,"uid":255155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"300e851a5376b09